{"tid":2132884,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有酒樓指需時準備食材 准日間堂食亦難即時恢復營業","createTime":"2020-07-30T15:55:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T15:56:40.000Z","uid":166360,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cf06d0c334175947b776cb17e00ef6f081ad4b44","tid":2132884,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T15:55:47.000Z","msg":"有酒樓指需時準備食材 准日間堂食亦難即時恢復營業<br />\n3小時前<br />\n<br />\n&quot;【Now新聞台】食肆將恢復日間堂食，餐飲業界批評政府朝令夕改，令業界難以適應。<br />\n<br />\n全日禁堂食，市民想好好吃餐飯都難，星期五開始，早午餐終於可再坐入食肆。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;有酒樓負責人就指，需時準備食材，即使政府公布可恢復日間堂食都難以配合。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=399942\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D399942&d=PqSGdtEI7oeKzC3efZxDSkuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=97e91665\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D399942&h=09d03730\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=399942</a>"},{"pid":"e07c95994ba4223c51f24a9a7de2f8ef6d71514e","tid":2132884,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T15:56:40.000Z","msg":"可憐哪.gif"}]}